{
  "name": "Military Ration Pill",
  "type": "consumable",
  "img": "icons/commodities/gems/pearl-beige-smooth.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span id=\"page201R_mcid9\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\">An edible pill that contains a drug designed to super </span><span dir=\"ltr\">charge the</span> <span dir=\"ltr\">person who consumes it, bodies, </span><span dir=\"ltr\">regeneration speed.</span> </span></p>\n<p><span id=\"page201R_mcid9\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\">Consuming a military ration pill </span><span dir=\"ltr\">takes a bonus action.</span> </span></p>\n<p><span id=\"page201R_mcid9\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\">A</span> <span dir=\"ltr\">c</span><span dir=\"ltr\">reature who takes this pill gains </span><span dir=\"ltr\">Temporary</span> <span dir=\"ltr\">Hit</span> <span dir=\"ltr\">&amp; Chakra</span> <span dir=\"ltr\">points</span> <span dir=\"ltr\">equal to the quality </span><span dir=\"ltr\">taken</span> <span dir=\"ltr\">for 1 hour.</span></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"page201R_mcid9\" class=\"markedContent\"> <span dir=\"ltr\">Taking another dosage of this item does </span><span dir=\"ltr\">not</span> <span dir=\"ltr\">stack.</span> <br /><span dir=\"ltr\">I</span><span dir=\"ltr\">nstead, it will replace however much you </span><span dir=\"ltr\">originally had. </span></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"page201R_mcid9\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\">You cannot gain the benefit of this Pill </span><span dir=\"ltr\">more than twice in a single 24</span><span dir=\"ltr\">-</span><span dir=\"ltr\">hour Perio</span><span dir=\"ltr\">d.</span></span></p>",
